---
import { site } from "../site.config";
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="wrap about-inner">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Why hire a solo contractor over an agency.</h2>
      <p class="section-lede">
        {/* TODO: rewrite in your own voice if this misses the mark / add a real bio + photo. */}
        I'm {site.ownerName}, and {site.name} is how I take on contract and
        freelance work after ten years building production frontends: React,
        TypeScript and Node projects, plus the API design and management
        that keeps them fed. Every project on this page is something I
        designed, built and shipped alone, front to back. That's also how I
        work with clients: one person who owns the whole problem, not a
        hand-off between three specialists.
      </p>
      <p class="section-lede">
        The games are here because gaming is a genuine passion of mine, not
        a gimmick. And the Japanese running through half these projects
        comes from a daily habit of studying the language and the culture
        behind it. I do my best work at the intersection of things I
        actually care about, and that's what a client gets too.
      </p>
    </div>
    <ul class="stats">
      <li><strong>10y</strong><span>professional React / TypeScript / NodeJS experience, including API management</span></li>
      <li><strong>6</strong><span>shipped side projects, all live in this portfolio</span></li>
      <li><strong>0</strong><span>hand-offs: one person designs, builds, and ships</span></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 56px;
  }

  .stats {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 26px;
    align-self: center;
  }

  .stats li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding-left: 18px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .stats strong {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .stats span {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
